Dialogue: 30,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Amadeus and Salieri...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu and me...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One was gifted with\Nnatural talent, Amadeus Mozart.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:25.69,0:00:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The other viewed him as\Na lifelong rival, Antonio Salieri.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,K331.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:34.20,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mozart's Piano Sonata No. 11\Nin A Major, first movement.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:39.03,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You like Mozart's music?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I dabble in it sometimes.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:43.66,0:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the quote “Death means not\Ngetting to listen to Mozart anymore.”
Dialogue: 30,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of that one.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:50.67,0:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Strictly speaking, there's no record\Nthat Einstein ever said those words.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:56.39,0:00:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I think it's a very logical statement.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:59.68,0:01:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Logical?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you can't listen\Nto Mozart if you're dead.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that much obvious?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is obvious.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:08.98,0:01:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you die, you can't listen.\NThe statement is true.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:13.78,0:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Logical, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:18.16,0:01:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,July 28, 2010...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:21.99,0:01:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu left this world.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:26.54,0:01:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amadeus and Salieri...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:28.63,0:01:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two hold a very special meaning to me.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:37.05,0:01:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved Kurisu...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:44.64,0:01:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I respected Kurisu...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I aspired to be like Kurisu...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:31.00,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Global Brain Science\NOrganization Office Prep Room.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A fundraising plea by Leskinen.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:37.38,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If everyone who read this donated\Njust one dollar, I could eat a can of oden.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:43.34,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Professor never\Ngets tired of joking around...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:48.43,0:03:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Maho! Welcome to\Nour powered-up prep room!
Dialogue: 30,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By that you mean the table and couch?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:55.11,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It is said, “Keeping it simple is the\Nsecret on the long journey towards truth.”
Dialogue: 30,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose quote is that?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be mine.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So? How's Amadeus?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished running the final checks.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to launch without issue.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:14.79,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I start it?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Senpai.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? No problems so far?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:29.10,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Not as far as I'm aware, at the least.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll let Okabe-san know we're good.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:37.19,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Though even if you say I'm restored,\NI'm not sure he'll want to talk to me...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he enjoys talking\Nto you a whole lot more.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to like it too.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:51.29,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you stop saying stuff like that?\NI'm telling you, it's not true!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:55.92,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After lengthy observation and analysis,\NI'm certain that I'm correct.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:00.46,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How so? You're just letting delusions\Nof love run amok in your head.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure missed you two going at it.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:13.43,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we get our meeting started?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:32.41,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This room's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:35.71,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Okabe-san? You're here early.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:47.76,0:05:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did the room go?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worse than it was a few days ago.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The lapse of time changes\Nboth people and things.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Functional, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I could go exploring in here!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:01.27,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, Amadeus is all restored now.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:06.53,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What will it be? If you want to\Nkeep testing, I can reset it for you.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, please.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Really?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened since then...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:28.01,0:06:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time I moved forward.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:32.97,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why Faris told me to bring\NMayuri along when I came?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Mayushii has a brilliant mind!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:41.81,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I get Faris-chan!\NShe must've wanted this room to be cleaned!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're here, it'll get cleaned?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:49.11,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, if Mayushii comes over,\Nshe'll think to bring that person along!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sergeant Clean!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:02.50,0:07:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be your drill instructor!\NRefer to me as Sergeant Clean!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Nae, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:13.09,0:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! Until this room is clean,\Nyou are nothing more than inchworms!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All you're good for is squirming\Naround on top of leaves!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the lowest life form on Earth!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:29.19,0:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to cleaning,\NNae-chan's personality changes a little.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's putting it lightly...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:35.87,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But when cleaning's over, maybe she'll\Nopen up and act all mushy and sweet!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you here?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?! Which of you\Nsaid something creepy?!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was me!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you smirking for?!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:50.51,0:07:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! From now on, you're Mr. Smileybear!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, Mr. Smileybear?!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Nae-sama!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it, Mr. Smileybear.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:00.31,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go sweep up and down\Nthe hall 10 times in 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nae-sama, yes, Nae-sama!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's enjoying every second of this...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are we doing here?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:13.20,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we're done, Hiyajo-san\Nand Kiryu-san are supposed to leave.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No one told me.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:20.25,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders from the honyaner. Can't refuse.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:24.96,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,—Not nearly good enough, Mr. Smileybear!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,—Well? Did you figure out anything new?\N—Not nearly good enough, Mr. Smileybear!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,—Well? Did you figure out anything new?\N—It's not?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No progress, sadly.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:30.76,0:08:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a guess about the culprits,\Nbut no way to know for sure.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't let it end up like SERN...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,SERN?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's... Forget it...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:40.10,0:08:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I find it hard to believe.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:43.35,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined Kurisu\Nwas researching time machines...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say you were lying.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:50.07,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On one hand it seems crazy,\Nbut nothing from her surprises me.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Salieri?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:57.41,0:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my user name at university.\NDidn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:01.29,0:09:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Does it have some special meaning?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:05.96,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Antonio Salieri.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:11.00,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The man whose life was thrown into chaos\Nby Amadeus Mozart... Do you know him?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the movie, right? I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:20.51,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Salieri had a promising future as a musician,
Dialogue: 30,0:09:24.23,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but he grew envious of Mozart's talents\Nand was driven into despair.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:28.65,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the hounding and\Npressure from Salieri led to his demise.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyajo-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:37.61,0:09:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I don't believe\Nthat's the case myself, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:55.34,0:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I'm AI.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:04.93,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... It just doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to fix it to my liking later.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The others will kill you\Nif they hear you say that.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:15.99,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin! Sorry to keep you!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell asleep, huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:20.24,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! Being Sergeant Clean\Nmust take it all out of her.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to carry her?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, if you want to eat a full-powered\Nstraight right from Tennouji-san.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:30.54,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Full-powered straight right! Huff huff...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All that drill training\Nmust've scrambled his head...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:38.38,0:10:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So... If you can't find something\Nyou need, let me know!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Where are Faris-san and Kiryu-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'll be right back.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said don't call me that.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... What's with the bag?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:56.82,0:11:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to shop.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:00.15,0:11:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but tonight is no boys allowed!\NNot even Kyouma, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No boys allowed?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, nya! The operation\Nin store for tonight is...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The All-Night Cinderella Girls Secret Party!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:14.63,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So sleepy someone slips secrets, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:21.97,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, you two?\NWhere's your excitement, nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:26.06,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! I even picked out some pricey\Nice cream and cake for us, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about Maho-nyan is,
Dialogue: 30,0:11:35.61,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,she's cute like a doll so\Neverything looks good on her, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:39.19,0:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit calling me that.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiryu-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Moe-nyan finally laughed, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What incredible boobs, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:50.37,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,These are just begging to be tickled, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:56.21,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! This is making me feel naughty, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,—N-No, stop! Ah! S-Stop!\N—I think she likes it!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting some juice, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you writing?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A memo... for my novel.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A novel? You're writing one?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:21.82,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, because I'm not special in any way.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:26.12,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically anyone can take my place.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:29.12,0:12:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou are you. Nobody can replace you.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be replaced,\Nso don't belittle yourself.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:37.92,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you compare yourself to others and\Nlive your whole life feeling inferior, that's so...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she likes it, nya...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:03.49,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened since then...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:07.12,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time I moved forward.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:23.92,0:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This circuit board pattern is\Nso pretty, it's like a work of art!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:28.01,0:13:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this an IFX008 image sensor?!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:34.56,0:13:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew Akihabara had places like this?!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the true Maho-senpai.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:40.11,0:13:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought\Nshe's so obsessed with parts?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love putting things together.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:45.74,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little, I made\NJapanese plastic models all the time.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:49.82,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you build a germanium radio?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Burned myself soldering one a good bit.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens to everyone!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:58.75,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I think it's only you two...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I not come here sooner?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've said it was like this!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you'd like it this much.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any more places like that one?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:13.51,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be stores like\Nthat all over the place, but lately...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, didn't you want to talk?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It can wait.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not busy, right?\NLet's hang out some more.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine with me, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An @channel character?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,@channel?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:41.42,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what? Kurisu had one\Nof these characters in her bedroom!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:45.46,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu did? She had one sent to America?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Say no more!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a closet @channeler for you...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:54.22,0:14:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?\NWhat's an @channeler?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nullpo...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserved it.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Care if I give it a shot?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:09.11,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I've just gotta use this arm\Nand drop it over the hole, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes nothing...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:19.37,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh! Why?! Why is it\Nbreaking the laws of physics?!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise they wouldn't profit from it.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty sure I loosened it up!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I'll get it for sure!\NI'm grabbing some change!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally suckered in...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be saying that!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:37.18,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you prove\Nyou're a man, Okabe-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! With this much I should be able...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:47.11,0:15:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An employee came by and loosened it a bit.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in me keeping it.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, in that case...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted it that badly?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After Kurisu passed away...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:06.54,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother knew Kurisu liked it so much,\Nso she put it in her room as a decoration.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was burned in the fire, so...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:17.81,0:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to give this\Nto Kurisu's mother as a present.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. That'd be nice...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, wanna go inside?\NThere's racing games too!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea we were there so long.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:39.58,0:16:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I had no idea you were\Nsuch a pro at racing games.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I might've got a bit carried away...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:48.84,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do next?\NGrab a bite or something?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:52.22,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's already getting pretty late.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:58.68,0:17:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's somewhere I have to visit\Nbefore I go back to America...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This place, huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... The place where\NMakise Kurisu lost her life.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:11.86,0:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The last place she was...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, just tell me where.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:16.53,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go in alone.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so quiet in here.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the shops have moved already,\Nsince it's going to be rebuilt.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really used much anymore.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in here.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So it was right here...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a physicist or anything,
Dialogue: 30,0:18:24.64,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't know the details\Nof the theory of relativity, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If space and time are unified,
Dialogue: 30,0:18:32.23,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,why can we move around in space,\Nbut not move freely through time?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:39.32,0:18:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I stand in the same\Nspatial axis where Kurisu died.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:44.45,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, just because the time axis is\Na little off, I can't stop it from happening.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop it.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:52.34,0:18:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you returned to the same time axis...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can't change anything.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:58.42,0:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you so sure?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:00.68,0:19:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I discussed it with Kurisu.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With Kurisu...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:19.95,0:19:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's my fault for lacking delicacy.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You cared for Kurisu so much that...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:26.79,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:29.71,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Did you really just\Nmeet her at a seminar?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem that way at all.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:37.67,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From time to time,\NI wonder how long it could've been.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:42.13,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One month? Two months? No...\NYou talk like you knew her well beyond that.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:50.06,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know so much about Kurisu?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:54.94,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I... Kurisu...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell something went on\Nyou don't want to talk about.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyajo-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:16.46,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see you,\NI think the same thing...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:20.67,0:20:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always look so sad?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing\Nwhen you talk about Kurisu.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same when you talk with everyone.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:29.89,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you're regretting some choice...\NAs if struggling alone against something...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's Mayuri-san and me...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:37.31,0:20:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're trying\Nto protect us from something.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:40.61,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thing is, we were really attacked...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:43.82,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it seems like to you?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:48.24,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to ask you\Nto tell me everything, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:52.62,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to support and\Nempower that feeling of yours, so...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:58.71,0:21:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised myself\NI wouldn't tell anybody, but I will.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have it.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu's...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu's legacy.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:12.77,0:21:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu's... legacy?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:17.48,0:21:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Her notebook computer.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With all her research data...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:22.82,0:21:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,With her theories... with her private data too.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Her own computer.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:29.28,0:21:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The thief that broke into\Nmy hotel must've been after that.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:35.29,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out her password,\Nso I'm having a trustworthy source analyze it.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:42.13,0:21:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That computer is Pandora's Box!\NIt mustn't be opened!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:45.88,0:21:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The data inside is a curse that leads\Nto the destruction of the world!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:52.60,0:21:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The race for a time machine is what\Nmakes Russia and America fight one another!
